newsitem.title: USA: LaserMaster to ship digital printer.
newsitem.headline: LaserMaster to ship digital printer.

text.p: LaserMaster Technologies Inc said Tuesday it expects to begin shipping a production-level model of its DesignWinder digital color printer by the end of the year.
The printer was displayed at a trade show last week and the company will ship limited quantities to technology partners in late September and October.

LaserMaster said it will begin shipping to various users and reseller sights by its second fiscal quarter ending December 1996, as design and production plans are finalized within the next 60 to 90 days.
